#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Kirjeldus"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:58
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<command>kbuildsycoca5</command> builds binary cache of the data stored "
#| "in <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and MIME type <literal "
#| "role=\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses "
#| "to find plugins, applications and other services."
msgid ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca6</command> builds binary cache of the data stored in "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> and &MIME; type <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal> files that the KService framework uses to find "
"plugins, applications and other services."
msgstr ""
"<command>kbuildsycoca5</command> ehitab andmete, mis on salvestatud <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal>- ja MIME tüüpide <literal role="
"\"extension\">.xml</literal>-failidesse, binaarse vahemälu, mida KService'i "
"raamistik kasutab pluginate, rakenduste ja muude teenuste leidmiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The KService library uses this database to efficiently provide the "
"information requested of it."
msgstr ""
"KService'i teek kasutab seda andmebaasi sellelt nõutava teabe tõhusaks "
"pakkumiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Users do not normally need to run this application directly; KService will "
"run it if necessary, when any of the files whose data is cached are changed."
msgstr ""
"Kasutajatel pole üldjuhul tarvidust seda rakendust vahetult kasutada. "
"KService käitab seda vajaduse korral, kui näiteks mõni failidest, mille "
"andmed on puhverdatud, muutub."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Võtmed"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "--global"
msgstr "--global"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
#| "currently only supported on Unix systems."
msgid ""
"Ignores any user-set files (in <varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). This is "
"currently only supported on &UNIX; systems."
msgstr ""
"Eiratakse igasuguseid kasutaja määratud faile (asukohas "
"<varname>XDG_DATA_HOME</varname>). Praegu on see toetatud ainult Unixi "
"süsteemides."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "--noincremental"
msgstr "--noincremental"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Rather than using the existing cache and only updating the information that "
"has changed or been added, start with an empty cache. Ignored if <option>--"
"global</option> is set."
msgstr ""
"Olemasoleva vahemälu kasutamise ja selle ainult siis uuendamise asemel, kui "
"midagi on muudetud või lisatud, alustamine tühja vahemäluga. Seda eiratakse, "
"kui määratud on võti <option>--global</option>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "--menutest"
msgstr "--menutest"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test the generation of the application menu database. Does not actually "
"build the cache."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduste menüü andmebaasi genereerimise test. Vahemälu tegelikult ei "
"ehitata."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "--testmode"
msgstr "--testmode"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the QStandardPaths \"test mode\" to avoid interfering with user data. "
"This is intended for use with unit tests."
msgstr ""
"QStandardPathsi kasutamine \"testrežiimis\", et mitte segada kasutaja "
"andmeid. See on eelkõige mõeldud ühiktestide tarbeks."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "--track <replaceable>menu-id</replaceable>"
msgstr "--track <replaceable>menüü ID</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbuildsycoca6.8.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
